| Task queued | `TaskCreated` | `websocket.rs` after each `enqueue_job` |

Each event gets a corresponding `emit_*` method on `PluginRuntime`, a Python `on_*` API function registered in `populate_api_module`, and a test verifying the callback fires correctly.
